snippet.title: Flappy Bird Arcade Game
snippet.description:
Downloaded over 50 million times, the Flappy Bird app is now life size! Bay Tek’s licensed Flappy Bird is sure to draw attention with the larger-than-life screen and a game play that will have players coming back for more. 

To learn more about this game please click here.
